{"tid":1104831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普下月訪日 傳參觀出雲號護衞艦及與新日皇會面","createTime":"2019-04-13T12:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T12:10:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"892ffe6ab23196d643f4e4057e011290f1271484","tid":1104831,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/04/13/2110362_1bffb67944e7087c8ca2fc125037ffc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F04%2F13%2F2110362_1bffb67944e7087c8ca2fc125037ffc7.jpg&h=340ba78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普將於下月訪問日本，據報他可能會參觀即將「航空母艦化」的「出雲號」護衞艦。<br />\n<br />\n《共同社》引述消息人士報道，日本政府計劃安排特朗普在下月訪日期間，與首相安倍晉三一起觀看相撲比賽，同時考慮在特朗普視察美國海軍橫須賀基地時，邀請他參觀將改裝成航母的「出雲號」護衞艦，彰顯牢固的日美同盟。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普將於下月26日至28日訪問日本，與安倍晉三舉行會談，預料他將是首位與新日皇會面的國賓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2110362/特朗普下月訪日+傳參觀出雲號護衞艦\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2110362%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E8%A8%AA%E6%97%A5%2B%E5%82%B3%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%B2%E8%99%9F%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%9E%E8%89%A6&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=bfd67c17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2110362/特朗普下月訪日+傳參觀出雲號護衞艦</a>"},{"pid":"4dc65ed7b285d4daa02ffae046f069e36a2ddb5c","tid":1104831,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會順便見埋肥金或者雜種？"},{"pid":"6f6c127a06c6ad40645e24dfc0f0ff6a4eee84e9","tid":1104831,"uid":130143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"念起上次餵金魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}